description: The clean finish of the Kate and Laurel Gabi Planter Set is designed to provide a beautiful stand-alone statement by presenting a lighter, airy display for your favorite houseplants. The clean modern finish creates an upscale look that will go with many different types of decor. The larger container is 11 inches in diameter and 9 inches tall. The smaller pot has a 7.5-inch diameter and is 8 inches tall. The height of this stand set allows for plants to spill over the sides. The larger pot sits within a 27.25-inch high metal base, and the smaller container sits within its base at 25 inches high from the floor. Each container can be easily removed from its stand if needed.
